headline: Coordinated Care Helps Students Create a Culture of Belonging on National No One Eats Alone Day with Seattle Seahawks Legend Walter Jones
summary: Coordinated Care, a Washington managed care organization and wholly owned subsidiary of Centene Corporation (NYSE: CNC) is partnering with Seattle Seahawks legend Pro Football Hall of Famer Walter Jones again this year to celebrate No One Eats Alone Day on February 12, with 6th graders from Illahee Middle School in Federal Way.
